description.value:
Homunculi scuplted to look like a genderless baby with implanted augmetic wings and a grav generator. Disturbing to some, can perform simple tasks such as copy text, fetching objects, carrying items, and singing The Emperor's praises.

Requirements

See Bestiary or Inquisitor's Handbook Page 192/193

Effect: Rare

Notes: 300 T
